        <content type="html" xml:base="https://aw2.help/builds/condi-soulbeast-daggers/">&lt;p&gt;The purpose of writing this guide is to provide a no-weapon swap method to play a melee PVE soulbeast while easily hitting the 70% benchmark with minimal effort. This build is low cognition, has few repetitions but has a relatively moderate APM. Only two CC skills need to be spaced out, while the rest of the skills are used on cooldown. Because this build scales to both condi and power, Vicious Quarry, a power trait is taken.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The juvenile bee is essential for this build and cannot be swapped out.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
