	data-armory-ids=&quot;93105&quot;
	data-armory-93105-stat=&quot;1067&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;td&gt;&lt;td&gt;Ring&lt;&#x2F;td&gt;&lt;td&gt; Sinister&lt;&#x2F;td&gt;&lt;&#x2F;tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;items&quot;
	data-armory-ids=&quot;91234&quot;
	data-armory-91234-stat=&quot;1067&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;td&gt;&lt;td&gt;Ring&lt;&#x2F;td&gt;&lt;td&gt; Sinister&lt;&#x2F;td&gt;&lt;&#x2F;tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;items&quot;
	data-armory-ids=&quot;100849&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;td&gt;&lt;td&gt;Relic&lt;&#x2F;td&gt;&lt;td&gt; Aristocracy &lt;&#x2F;td&gt;&lt;&#x2F;tr&gt;&lt;&#x2F;tbody&gt;&lt;&#x2F;table&gt;
&lt;hr&#x2F;&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;small&gt;Relic of Aristocracy can be procced through auto-attacks, therefore your mainhand must be dagger most of the time.&lt;&#x2F;small&gt;&lt;br&#x2F;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;small&gt;Swapping all your Viper&#x27;s (HoT-only Set) pieces to Celestial (Core Set)) will lead to a small DPS loss (&amp;lt;10%).&lt;&#x2F;small&gt;&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;small&gt;Grieving pieces may be added in place of Sinister Pieces&lt;&#x2F;small&gt;&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ul&gt;
&lt;h4 id=&quot;weapon-swap&quot;&gt;Weapon Swap&lt;&#x2F;h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Weapon swap is optional but not recommended unless situationally used&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Shortbow (Ranged&#x2F;CC)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ol&gt;
&lt;h4 id=&quot;infusions&quot;&gt;Infusions&lt;&#x2F;h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;items&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;39337&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Malign Infusion OR&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;items&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;39620&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Mighty +5 Agony Infusion&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ul&gt;
&lt;hr &#x2F;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a rel=&quot;noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; href=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;gw2skills.net&#x2F;editor&#x2F;?POgAgilZUw+YSMKmJW6P3P&#x2F;cc4+4R7A-DSRYfB5ZGNchjR8EIUBY4FQACXD8aSxZFoC-e&quot;&gt;GW2Skills Link&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;h4 id=&quot;food&quot;&gt;Food&lt;&#x2F;h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;items&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;91876&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Salsa-Topped Veggie Flatbread&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;items&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;91878&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Cilantro and Cured Meat Flatbread&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;items&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;91804&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Spherified Cilantro Oyster Soup&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;items&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;43361&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Koi Cake(budget alternative)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;small&gt;The difference between the various ascended food is minimal.&lt;&#x2F;small&gt;&lt;br&#x2F;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ul&gt;
&lt;h4 id=&quot;utility&quot;&gt;Utility&lt;&#x2F;h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;items&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;48917&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Toxic Tuning Crystal&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ul&gt;
&lt;h4 id=&quot;pets&quot;&gt;Pets&lt;&#x2F;h4&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The Janthiri Bee is competitive in damage and provides ready access CC, making it the default best option for raiding.&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ol&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;blockquote&gt;
&lt;hr &#x2F;&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;build&quot;&gt;Build&lt;&#x2F;h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Condi DPS\&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;pre data-lang=&quot;chatlink&quot; class=&quot;language-chatlink z-code&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-chatlink&quot; data-lang=&quot;chatlink&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;z-source z-chatlink&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;z-punctuation z-definition z-string z-begin&quot;&gt;[&amp;amp;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;DQQePSE3Ny55AAAAvwAAAOkWAAAbAAAALhYAAEclAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAACLwBrAAA=&lt;span class=&quot;z-punctuation z-definition z-string z-end&quot;&gt;]&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;code&gt;&lt;&#x2F;pre&gt;
&lt;hr &#x2F;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;peticon&quot; style=&quot;background: url(&#x27;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;render.guildwars2.com&#x2F;file&#x2F;DF96C29EFA4BDEC66C3149F280141490C20458D3&#x2F;52606.png&#x27;) 50% 50% no-repeat;&quot;&gt;Juvenile Warthog&lt;&#x2F;div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;peticon&quot; style=&quot;background: url(&#x27;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;render.guildwars2.com&#x2F;file&#x2F;03BF0B1C079C06B359E0CE520E747AC5E878F395&#x2F;3594054.png&#x27;) 50% 50% no-repeat;&quot;&gt;Juvenile Janthiri Bee&lt;&#x2F;div&gt;&lt;div data-armory-embed=&#x27;skills&#x27; data-armory-ids=&#x27;31914,12537,40498,12476,45717&#x27;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;div&gt;&lt;div data-armory-embed=&#x27;specializations&#x27; data-armory-ids=&#x27;30,33,55&#x27; data-armory-30-traits=&#x27;1069,1846,1888&#x27; data-armory-33-traits=&#x27;1099,1101,1701&#x27; data-armory-55-traits=&#x27;2071,2161,2128&#x27;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;div&gt;
&lt;hr &#x2F;&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;rotation-and-utilities&quot;&gt;Rotation and Utilities&lt;&#x2F;h2&gt;
&lt;h4 id=&quot;dps-rotation&quot;&gt;DPS Rotation&lt;&#x2F;h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Stay merged at all times.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Pre-battle -  &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;12476&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Spike Trap + &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;12537&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Sharpening Stone (up to 30s before fight starts)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;General Rotation - Use all skills on cooldown except healing and CC skills.&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Spread out &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;75771&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Bumble, &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;12476&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Spike Trap to maintain  &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;traits&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;2127&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Twice as Vicious
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;12476&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Spike Trap on cooldown.&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Delay &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;75771&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Bumble.&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ul&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ol&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;blockquote&gt;
&lt;h4 id=&quot;crowd-control&quot;&gt;Crowd Control&lt;&#x2F;h4&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;75771&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Bumble and &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;12476&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Spike Trap are part of your rotation.&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You may switch to a shortbow temporarily if you require CC.&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ol&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;blockquote&gt;
&lt;h4 id=&quot;sustainability&quot;&gt;Sustainability&lt;&#x2F;h4&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Swapping all your Vipers pieces to Celestial only reduces your DPS by 5%. This is an efficient way to maintain high DPS and survive harder encounters in open world.&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You may opt to use Oyster-based ascended food or birthday cake.&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ol&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;blockquote&gt;
&lt;hr &#x2F;&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;benchmark&quot;&gt;Benchmark&lt;&#x2F;h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The build is benched with ascended but without infusions. You should be able to achieve 32.5k DPS with infusions at the golem.&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;For benching or if playing solo, pick &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;traits&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;2143&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Oppressive Superiority.&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;It is not possible to bench with allies unless you have a friend to assist you.&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ul&gt;
</content>
        
    </entry>
