        <content type="html" xml:base="https://aw2.help/builds/condi-soulbeast/">&lt;p&gt;The purpose of writing this guide is to provide a no-weapon swap method to play a ranged PVE soulbeast while easily hitting the 70% benchmark with minimal effort. This build is low cognition, has few repetitions but has a relatively moderate APM. The skills do not require specific timing and having extra hard CC in the build allows flexible upkeep of &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;traits&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;2127&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Twice as Vicious, which has a rather tight timing on other builds. This is inspired by the Guild Wars 1 skill &lt;a rel=&quot;noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; href=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;wiki.guildwars.com&#x2F;wiki&#x2F;Barbed_Arrows&quot;&gt;Barbed Arrows&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The juvenile bee does decent condition damage with a very decent extra 300 points of CC.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
